msgstr "当你上传新图片时，Odoo自动压缩以减少大小（PNG和GIF无损压缩，JPG有损压缩）。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/pages/seo.rst:343
msgid ""
"From the upload button, you have the option to keep the original image "
